### Topic: [Two Sum Problem](https://leetcode.com/problems/two-sum/)

### Problem Statement: 
> Given an array of integers, return indices of the two numbers such that they add up to a specific target.

You can find the original question here -> [Two Sum Problem](https://leetcode.com/problems/two-sum/)
