### [Two sum - Leet code solution in Python Language.](https://dev.to/codeperfectplus/two-sum-leet-code-solution-452d)

```python
class Solution:
    def twoSum(self, nums: List[int], target: int) -> List[int]:
        seen = {}

        for index, num in enumerate(nums):
            other = target - num 

            if other in seen:
                return[seen[other],index]
            else:
                seen[num] = index
        return []
```

